{{about|河流|地區|梅吉專區}}
'''梅吉河'''（Mechi River），又譯'''米其河'''<ref>《地界地圖集 第二冊：亞洲與俄國》，國防研究院、中國地學研究所，1968年</ref>，是流經[[尼泊爾|尼泊爾]]與[[印度|印度]]的跨界河流，為[[默哈嫩達河|默哈嫩達河]]的支流。

梅吉河發源於尼泊爾的{{link-en|瑪哈巴拉特山脈|Lower Himalayan Range}}。它流經尼泊爾東南部，成為尼泊爾與印度的界河，隨後流入印度[[比哈爾邦|比哈爾邦]]，最終在[[基商甘傑縣|基商甘傑縣]]注入默哈嫩達河。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://emily7787.wikispaces.com/file/view/Five+Themes+of+Geography+Master.pdf| title=Five Themes of Geography| work=Rivers| first=| last=| publisher=| accessdate=2010-05-22| archive-date=2011-07-18| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718051221/http://emily7787.wikispaces.com/file/view/Five+Themes+of+Geography+Master.pdf| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = | title = http://www.newworldencyclopedia.org/entry/Gurkha_War |  title=Gurkha War | work = | first=  | last=  | publisher = New World Encyclopaedia |accessdate = 2010-05-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url =http://kishanganj.bih.nic.in/river.htm |title =Kishanganj district |work = |first = |last = |publisher =Kishanganj district administration |accessdate =2010-05-22 |deadurl =yes |archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20100408074040/http://kishanganj.bih.nic.in/river.htm |archivedate =2010-04-08 }}</ref>

